replaceStrings.replace: Measures the completion rate of your ad against the completion norm, showing the performance of your ad relative to an average ad of the same type. The average is represented by a score of 100, within a range from 0 to 200.
represents the Attention of a specific creative or program placement vs the average. The average is represented by a score of 100, and the total index range is from 0 through 200.

Wear is determined by looking at the percent drop in attention over time compared to the peak attention across the lifetime of the ad. This is calculated using a 3-day moving average and reported on as None, Light, Medium and Heavy.
